{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1496170, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "明明就应该公平抽签，为啥你们觉得朋友多/钱多就应该抽中概率更大？", "timestamp": 1619001541, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496180, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496170, "tag": null, "text": "#  “公平”？", "timestamp": 1619001668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496170, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 从一开始就不是公平，谢谢您嘞", "timestamp": 1619001741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496194, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496191, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 为啥不是公平？", "timestamp": 1619001757, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496195, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496191, "tag": null, "text": "抽签部分至少是公平", "timestamp": 1619001771, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496198, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496195, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 然而你们想把它弄成不公平", "timestamp": 1619001783, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496226, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496198, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 卖的人想出，买的人愿意掏钱，不公平的地方在哪", "timestamp": 1619001970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496247, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496195, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 抽签部分公平？叫公平？", "timestamp": 1619002112, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496261, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496226, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 卖的人为什么可以从学校免费资源中获利呢？如果不想去看，可否通过官方渠道把票无偿转让给其他想去看的同学。\n或许低年级的同学可能不知道，原来选课还是抢课拼手速，因此就出现了抢课后进行出售的现象，我还见到有个同学把1学分的文素课卖了50元。这和这次抢票也是差不多的吧，这真的合理吗？", "timestamp": 1619002183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496262, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496247, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 分院系", "timestamp": 1619002186, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496282, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496261, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 从他抽到的那一刻起，他就已经获利了", "timestamp": 1619002285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496286, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496261, "tag": null, "text": "让人白白放走已经到手的利益恐怕是很难的事", "timestamp": 1619002326, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496290, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496261, "tag": null, "text": "最后的结果就是上座率降低，想看的同学也没看上", "timestamp": 1619002347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496282, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 因为这是在规则范围之外", "timestamp": 1619002365, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496300, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496286, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 所以通过严格查票的方式让他放弃", "timestamp": 1619002404, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496301, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496261, "tag": null, "text": "# Re Dave: 免费资源怎么了？是从一开始全体学生都公平吗？既得利益者在喊公平？", "timestamp": 1619002414, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496297, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我承认确实违反规则，但要抽到票的同学退票恐怕很难，宁愿拿着票不去或者送给认识的人碰运气", "timestamp": 1619002425, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496390, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "官方误杀了几个人你就把身边所有你看不顺眼的人都杀了？", "timestamp": 1619003097, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496413, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496390, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 卖票损失了谁的利益？就算不卖也没几个人会把票交回去的", "timestamp": 1619003316, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496624, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496413, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 损失了以后所有这种活动的意向参与者 因为可以卖出去 所以以后不管去不去都会先抢了再说 比如人群中本来只有100个人感兴趣的活动 卖票导致虽然每次都是这100个人参加 但是每次都有500人在抢票 然后卖给这100人 说白了就是校内黄牛 哪来那么多理直气壮", "timestamp": 1619004725, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496728, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496624, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace:供不应求，正常现象而已，强行压票真的只会导致资源浪费", "timestamp": 1619005545, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496903, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496728, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 笑死 现在有人已经成学生🐂了不是吗 谁还不是经管的学生了 考上大学的名额你怎么不鼓励合法交易呢 有人买肯定会有人卖啊 器官也是 不让买卖器官会有人死啊 买卖一下也不会有人死啊 有点好笑。与其这样干脆建议学校以后这种活动所有票都拍卖算了 价最高的几千人得到票 多稳啊", "timestamp": 1619006949, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496910, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496728, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 查票的同学有什么牛的 有钱的同学才是真的nb啊", "timestamp": 1619007001, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1499475, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 294293, "reply_to": 1496910, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 有钱的同学确实是真的nb", "timestamp": 1619026805, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 294293, "reply": 24, "tag": null, "text": "查票的同学你们好nbnb?", "timestamp": 161900